<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">DTC Force has achieved the Salesforce Summit Partner status. It is an honor that speaks volumes about our commitment and passion for excellence in digital transformation and customer relationship management. This means we are part of an exclusive group of 1% firms globally to have achieved the Salesforce Summit status.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We are reflecting on our journey since DTC Force came to life in 2014. After all, it is hard not to have mixed emotions at this moment as we feel immense pride, gratitude, and excitement. We are not only sharing the news but also celebrating a milestone that marks a significant chapter in our story.</span></p>
<h2><b>A Look Back on Our Journey</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We knew we were on to something special from our first project. Fast forward to now, with over 800 projects under our belt, each one has been a step towards greater innovation and deeper customer relationships. Our journey has been about more than just numbers; it’s been about the trust you’ve placed in us and the solutions we’ve crafted together. Our 5-star rating on the <a href="https://appexchange.salesforce.com/appxConsultingListingDetail?listingId=a0N3A00000FABHgUAP">Salesforce App Exchange</a> is a testament to this trust and the quality we strive to deliver daily.</span></p>
<h2><b>The team behind achieving</b><b> Salesforce Summit Partner Status</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our incredible team has been the backbone of our success. Their <a href="https://dtcforce.com/expertise/">expertise</a>, creativity, and dedication have propelled us forward, project by project. Their hard work has enabled us to tackle challenges and, as a result, deliver the transformative solutions our clients rely on. Our capable team boasts 100+ Salesforce Certifications and is battle-hardened with a variety of cross-cloud custom CRM implementations.</span></p>
<h2><b>Expanding Our Horizons</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’ve grown from our initial roots in Canada to simultaneously establishing a presence in other regions as well. We have a presence in the United States, Saudi Arabia, and the United Arab Emirates at this point. This expansion has brought us closer to newer markets, offering localized support and understanding the unique needs of each market.</span></p>
<h2><b>A Word from Our CEO, Zameer Mulla</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">“Our achievement of Salesforce Summit Partner status reflects our collective journey. It’s about the hard work, the partnerships, and the innovation we’ve shared since our inception. This milestone is not just ours; it belongs to every client, every team member, and every supporter who has been part of our story.”</span></p>
<h2><b>Looking to expand with S</b><b>alesforce Summit Partner Status</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’re also gearing up for what’s next as we celebrate this achievement. With even greater access to Salesforce resources, training, and technology, we’re excited about the opportunities to bring even more value to our projects and partnerships.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’re here because of you. Your trust, support, and collaboration have been the driving force behind our success. As we continue to navigate the future of digital transformation together, we’re excited about the possibilities that lie ahead.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Thank you for being a part of our DTC Force family. Here’s to many more milestones together!</span></p>
